{"obj_edit_time":"1769150204","blocks":[{"block_id":"YGujdv8jWolHt5xfFxkjo083pCe","block_type":1,"children":["doxjp3p8aVmW1iYpos5KHqzljDg","doxjpatI6FDEmGgVRyK9pLytz5R","doxjp6BJf4Wv0uMoS597Op8nHzd","doxjpLwwnfNYaduON1TKYGlK2d7","doxjpbyY7j1iuaPX1FDYvtAlGKf","doxjpPfJrmLvVULkj3mOvSoJugf","doxjpKbqKt1obrqHbsqLb1IFkVd","doxjpyMQvvsRbVn1nAF9JuSsOre","doxjpddI403AVNlh2NJb4vAfBob","doxjpu0Z8yZeNwV5tY2i1aQns1g","doxjpnoy77EDlcixt9rWMggejZb","doxjpiZx6fmligFH8YIADnf8y6h"],"page":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"業務介紹","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1}},"parent_id":""},{"block_id":"doxjp3p8aVmW1iYpos5KHqzljDg","block_type":14,"code":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"slug: ThhLwRaCpiKqt1kOv0DcR4ajnmg\ntitle: 業務介紹\n","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}},{"text_run":{"content":"sidebar_position: 0","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"language":67,"wrap":false}},"parent_id":"YGujdv8jWolHt5xfFxkjo083pCe"},{"block_id":"doxjpatI6FDEmGgVRyK9pLytz5R","block_type":3,"heading1":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"業務介紹","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"YGujdv8jWolHt5xfFxkjo083pCe"},{"block_id":"doxjp6BJf4Wv0uMoS597Op8nHzd","block_type":3,"heading1":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"概述","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"YGujdv8jWolHt5xfFxkjo083pCe"},{"block_id":"doxjpLwwnfNYaduON1TKYGlK2d7","block_type":2,"parent_id":"YGujdv8jWolHt5xfFxkjo083pCe","text":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"證券行業的入金業務是指投資者向其證券賬戶中注入資金的過程。這是參與證券市場交易的必要步驟，投資者需要在證券賬戶中有足夠的資金才能買入股票、債券或其他證券產品。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}}},{"block_id":"doxjpbyY7j1iuaPX1FDYvtAlGKf","block_type":3,"heading1":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"入金步骤","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"YGujdv8jWolHt5xfFxkjo083pCe"},{"block_id":"doxjpPfJrmLvVULkj3mOvSoJugf","block_type":2,"parent_id":"YGujdv8jWolHt5xfFxkjo083pCe","text":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"入金業務的基本流程：","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}}},{"block_id":"doxjpKbqKt1obrqHbsqLb1IFkVd","block_type":2,"parent_id":"YGujdv8jWolHt5xfFxkjo083pCe","text":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"選擇證券經紀商","text_element_style":{"bold":true,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}},{"text_run":{"content":"： 投資者首先需要選擇一家證券經紀商，這是提供證券交易服務的金融機構。證券經紀商通常提供在線平台，使投資者能夠輕松進行交易和管理其證券賬戶。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}}},{"block_id":"doxjpyMQvvsRbVn1nAF9JuSsOre","block_type":2,"parent_id":"YGujdv8jWolHt5xfFxkjo083pCe","text":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"開立證券賬戶","text_element_style":{"bold":true,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}},{"text_run":{"content":"： 在選擇經紀商後，投資者需要完成開戶流程。這通常包括填寫相關的開戶申請表格、提供身份證明、地址證明等必要文件。一旦賬戶開立成功，投資者就能夠獲得一個唯一的賬戶號碼。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}}},{"block_id":"doxjpddI403AVNlh2NJb4vAfBob","block_type":2,"parent_id":"YGujdv8jWolHt5xfFxkjo083pCe","text":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"選擇入金方式","text_element_style":{"bold":true,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}},{"text_run":{"content":"： 證券經紀商通常提供多種入金方式，包括銀行轉賬、電匯、支票存款等。投資者可以根據自己的需求和方便程度選擇合適的入金方式。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}}},{"block_id":"doxjpu0Z8yZeNwV5tY2i1aQns1g","block_type":2,"parent_id":"YGujdv8jWolHt5xfFxkjo083pCe","text":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"進行入金操作","text_element_style":{"bold":true,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}},{"text_run":{"content":"： 投資者通過選擇合適的入金方式，將資金轉入其證券賬戶。這通常需要提供一些必要的信息，如轉賬金額、付款賬戶信息等。一些證券經紀商還可能要求進行身份驗證，以確保資金安全。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}}},{"block_id":"doxjpnoy77EDlcixt9rWMggejZb","block_type":2,"parent_id":"YGujdv8jWolHt5xfFxkjo083pCe","text":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"確認入金","text_element_style":{"bold":true,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}},{"text_run":{"content":"： 一旦資金成功轉入證券賬戶，投資者會收到確認通知，通常包括入金金額、入金日期等信息。這是確保資金正確到賬的重要步驟。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}}},{"block_id":"doxjpiZx6fmligFH8YIADnf8y6h","block_type":2,"parent_id":"YGujdv8jWolHt5xfFxkjo083pCe","text":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"開始交易","text_element_style":{"bold":true,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}},{"text_run":{"content":"： 一旦賬戶中有足夠的資金，投資者就可以開始進行證券交易。他們可以通過證券經紀商提供的交易平台買入或賣出股票、債券或其他證券產品。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}}}]}